      <h4 class="page-header" id="create">Create a conversation</h4>

      <pre>
curl -XPOST -H "Content-type: application/json" -d '{
  "conversation": {
    "distinct_id": "<span class="js-distinct-id"></span>",
    "properties": {
      "group": {
        "name": "Dialog",
        "distinct_id": "8721hnj234"
      }
    }
  }
}' 'https://api.dialoganalytics.com/v1/conversations?token=dialog-public-token'</pre>

